[{"Id": 1013975, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": 1, "EnglishDescription": "Sayyid Ibne Tawus has narrated in Mazaar that when one decides to perform the Ziyarat of Kazmain, it is advisable to first perform the ghusl and then he should proceed on the Ziyarat, with demenour and patience. Upon reaching the gate he should stop there and recite…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Sayyid Ibne Tawus ne Mazaar mein riwaayat ki hai, keh jab Kazmain ki ziyarat ka iraada karo to, pehle ghusl karo aur phir ziyarat ke liye rawaana ho sukoon o itmenaan ke saath. Jab rauze ke darwaaze par pohoncho’n to wahan khade ho kar is tarah se kaho…", "UrduDescription": "سید ابن طا ؤ س ؒ نے مزار میں نقل کیا ہے اس کی کیفیت یہ ہے : جب کو ئی شخص آپ کی زیا رت کر نا چاہے تو پہلے غسل کرے اور پھر آرام اور وقا ر کے ساتھ آہستہ آہستہ حضرتؑ کے حرم مبا ر ک کی طرف چلے اور جب دروازے پرپہنچے تو یہ کہے۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "A