icRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1013976, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Allah is the Most Great. Allah is the Most Great. There is no god save Allah. And Allah is the Most Great. All praise be to Allah for guiding [me] to His religion and for leading (me) successfully to His Course to which He has invited (us). O Allah, You are verily the most Honorable Besought One and the most Honorable Purposed One. I thus have come to You, seeking nearness to You in the name of the son of Your Prophet’s daughter, Your blessings be upon him and upon his immaculate fathers and pure sons. O Allah, (please) send blessings upon Muhammad and the Household of Muhammad, never frustrate my efforts, never cut off my hope, make me illustrious in Your view in this world as well as the world to come, and make me of those brought near to You.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Khuda buzurg-tar hai, Khuda buzurg-tar hai, Khuda ke siwa koi ma’bood nahi, Khuda buzurg-tar hai, hamd hai Khuda ke liye keh us ne apne deen ki rehnumaayi ki aur apne jis raaste ki taraf bulaaya us par chal ne ki taufiq di. Ay Ma’bood! Be-shak Tu behtareen maqsood hai aur Tu bohot achchha mehmaan nawaaz hai. Pas mai Teri baargah mein aaya keh Tera qurb haasil karu Tere Nabi ki dukhtar ke farzand ke waaste se un par Teri rehmat ho aur unke paakeeza aaba par aur unke paakeeza farzando’n par. Ay Ma’bood! Muhammad (s.a.w.a) aur unki paak Aal (a.s) par rehmat naazil farma aur meri koshish na-kaam na bana, meri ummeed na tod aur mujhe apne huzoor ba-izzat muqarrabo’n mein se qaraar de is duniya mein aur aalam’e aakherat mein.", "Urdu": "خدا بزر گ تر ہے خدا بزر گ تر ہے خدا کے سوا کوئی معبود نہیں خدا بزر گ تر ہے حمد ہے خداکے لئے کہ اس نے اپنے دین کی راہنما ئی کی اور اپنے جس راستے کی طرف بلا یا اس پر چلنے کی توفیق دی اے معبود! بے شک تو بہترین مقصود ہے اور تو بہت اچھا مہمان نواز ہے پس میں تیری بارگاہ میں آیا کہ تیری قربت حاصل کروں تیر ے نبی کی دختر کے فرزند کے واسطے سے ان پر تیری رحمتیں ہوں اور ان کے پاکیزہ آباء پر اور ان کے پاکیزہ فرزندوں پر اے معبود! محمدؐ اور اس کی پاک آلؑ پر رحمت نازل فرما اور میری کوشش ناکام نہ بنا میری امید نہ توڑ اور مجھے اپنے حضور باعزت قربتوں میں سے قرار دے اس دنیا میں اور عالَمِ آخرت میں۔", "RArabic": "ALLAAHO AKBARO AALAAHO AKBARO LAA ELAAHA ILLAL LAAHO WAL LAAHO AKBARO ALHAMDO LILLAAHE A’LAA HEDAAYATEHI LE DEENEHI WAT TAWFEEQE LEMAA DA-A’A ELAYHE MIN SABEELEHI ALLAAHUMMA INNAKA AKRAMO MAQSOODIN WA AKRAMO MAA-TIYYIN WA QAD ATAYTOKA MOTAQARREBAN ILAIKA BE-IBNE BINTE NABIYYEKA SALAWAATOKA A’LAIHE WA A’LAA AAA-BAA-EHIT TAAHEREENA WA ABNAAA-E-HIT TAYYEBEENA ALLAAHUMMA SALLE A’LAA MOHAMMADIN WA AALE MOHAMMADIN WA LAA TOKHAYYIB SA’YEE WA LAA TAQ-TA’ RAJAAA-EE WAJ-A’LNEE I’NDAKA WAJEEHAN FID DUNYAA WAL AAKHERATE WA MENAL MOQARRABEENA.", "ArabicText1": "اَللهُ اَكْبَرُ اَللهُ اَكْبَرُ لَا اِلٰهَ اِلَّا اللہُ وَاللہُ اَكْبَرُ۔ اَلْحَمْدُ لِلهِ عَلٰی هِدَایَتِهٖ لِدِیْنِهٖ وَالتَّوْفِیْقِ لِمَا دَعَا اِلَیْهِ مِنْ سَبِیْلِهٖ۔ اَللّٰهُمَّ اِنَّكَ اَكْرَمُ مَقْصُوْدٍ وَاَكْرَمُ مَاْتِیٍّ وَقَدْ اَتَیْتُكَ مُتَقَرِّبًا اِلَیْكَ بِاِبْنِ بِنْتِ نَبِیِّكَ صَلَوَاتُكَ عَلَیْهِ وَعَلٰٓی اٰبَآئِهِ الطَّاهِرِیْنَ وَاَبْنَآئِهِ الطَّیِّبِیْنَ۔ اَللّٰهُمَّ صَلِّ عَلٰی مُحَمَّدٍ وَّاٰلِ مُحَمَّدٍ وَّلَا تُخَیِّبْ سَعْیِیْ وَلَا تَقْطَعْ رَجَآئِیْ وَاجْعَلْنِیْ عِنْدَكَ وَجِیْهًا فِی الدُّنْیَا وَالْاٰخِرَۃِ وَمِنَ الْمُقَرَّبِیْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7"