edSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1013980, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah’s Messenger, may I enter? O Allah’s Prophet, may I enter? O Muhammad the son of Abdullah, may I enter? O Commander of the Faithful, may I enter? O Abu-Muhammad Hasan, may I enter? O Aba-Abdullah Husain, may I enter? O Abu-Muhammad Ali ibn Husain, may I enter? O Abu-Ja`far Muhammad ibn Ali, may I enter? O Abu Abdullah Ja`far ibn Muhammad, may I enter? O my master Abul Hasan Musa ibn Ja`far, may I enter? O my master Abu-Ja`far, may I enter? O my master Muhammad ibn Ali, may I enter?", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Kya mai andar aa jaawu ay Khuda ke Rasool (s.a.w.a)? Kya mai andar aa jaawu ay Khuda ke Nabi? Kya mai andar aa jaawu ay Muhammad bin Abdullah (s.a.w.a)? Kya mai andar aa jaawu ay Momino ke Ameer (a.s)? Kya mai andar aa jaawu ay Abu Muhammad Hasan (a.s)? Kya mai andar aa jaawu ay Abu Abdillah al-Husain (a.s)? Kya mai andar aa jaawu ay Abu Muhammad Ali ibne Husain (a.s)? Kya mai andar aa jaawu ay Abu Jafar Muhammad bin Ali (a.s)? Kya mai andar aa jaawu ay Abu Abdillah Jafar bin Muhammad (a.s)? Kya mai andar aa jaawu ay mere Maula Moosa ibne Jafar (a.s)? Kya mai andar aa jaawu ay mere Maula ay Abu Jafar (a.s)? Kya mai daakhil ho jaawu ay mere Maula Muhammad ibne Ali (a.s).", "Urdu": "کیا میں اند ر آجا ؤ ں اے خدا کے رسو ل ؐ ؟کیا میں اندر آجاؤں اے خدا کے نبیؐ؟ کیامیں اند ر آجاؤں اے محمدؐ ابن عبداللہ ؑکیا میں اندر آجاؤں اے مو منو ں کے امیرؑ ؟کیا میں اندر آجاؤ ں اے ابو محمد حسن ؑ؟کیا میں اندر آجاؤں اے ابو عبداللہ الحسینؑ ؟کیا میں اندر آجاؤں اےابو محمدؑ علیؑ ابن الحسینؑ ؟کیا میں اندر آجاؤں اے ابوجعفرؑ محمد ابن علیؑ؟ کیا میں اندر آجاؤں اے ابو عبداﷲؑ جعفر ابن محمدؑ ؟کیا میں اندر آجاؤں اے میرے مولیٰ موسیٰؑ ابن جعفرؑ کیا میں داخل ہو جاؤں اے میرے مولا اے ابوجعفرؑ ؟کیا میں داخل ہو جاؤں اے میرے مولا محمدؑ ابن علیؑ۔", "RArabic": "A-ADKHOLO YAA RASOOLAL LAAHE A-ADKHOLO YAA NABIYYAL LAAHE A-ADKHOLO YAA MOHAMMADABNA A’BDIL LAAHE A-ADKHOLO YAA AMEERAL MOMENEENA A-ADKHOLO YAA ABAA MOHAMMADENIL HASANA A-ADKHOLO YAA ABAA A’BDIL LAAHIL HUSAYNA A-ADKHOLO YAA ABAA MOHAMMADIN A’LIYYABNAL HUSAYNE A-ADKHOLO YAA ABAA JA’FARIN MOHAMMADABNA A’LIYYIN A-ADK